text: Winifred Cooper was a British film editor known for her work on films like They Met in the Dark and Hitchcock's Rich and Strange. == Selected filmography == * Candlelight in Algeria (1944) * They Met in the Dark (1943) * At Dawn We Die (1943) * Torpedoed (1937) * Two Who Dared (1936) * Bill and Coo (1931) * East of Shanghai (1931) * The Outsider (1931) == References == Category:British film editors Category:Women film editors Category:Year of birth missing Category:Year of death missing == External links == *
